EN: Used cars are sometimes more cost-effective than new cars.

ZH: 他不介意买一辆旧一点的二手车。
EN: He doesn't mind buying a slightly older used car.

ZH: 最近几年，二手车市场一直在增长。
EN: The used car market has been growing in recent years.

ZH: 这家汽车店里有各种各样的二手车。
EN: This car dealership has a variety of used cars.

